direction: right

Dev: {
  shape: person
  label: "Desenvolvedor"
}

Docker: {
  shape: rectangle
  label: "Docker\n(Dockerfile multi-stage)"
}

ECR: {
  shape: rectangle
  label: "Amazon ECR\n(Imagem da Lambda)"
}

AWS: {
  API_Gateway: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "API Gateway\n(POST /avaliacao)"
  }
  Lambda_Feedback: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "Lambda processarFeedback\n(Container Image - Java 17)"
  }
  DynamoDB: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "DynamoDB\n(Tabela Feedbacks)"
  }
  SNS: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "SNS\n(Notificações + Relatório)"
  }
  EventBridge: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "EventBridge\n(Cron semanal)"
  }
  Lambda_Report: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "Lambda gerarRelatorioSemanal\n(Container Image - Java 17)"
  }
  CloudWatch: {
    shape: rectangle
    label: "CloudWatch\n(Logs e Métricas)"
  }
}

Admin: {
  shape: person
  label: "Administrador"
}

User: {
  shape: person
  label: "Estudante"
}

Dev -> Docker: docker build
Docker -> ECR: docker push (via AWS CLI)
ECR -> AWS.Lambda_Feedback: image uri
ECR -> AWS.Lambda_Report: image uri

User -> AWS.API_Gateway: POST /avaliacao
AWS.API_Gateway -> AWS.Lambda_Feedback
AWS.Lambda_Feedback -> AWS.DynamoDB: put item
AWS.Lambda_Feedback -> AWS.SNS: publish (se nota < 5)
AWS.EventBridge -> AWS.Lambda_Report: invoke (cron)
AWS.Lambda_Report -> AWS.DynamoDB: scan última semana
AWS.Lambda_Report -> AWS.SNS: publish (relatório)
AWS.SNS -> Admin: e-mail
AWS.Lambda_Feedback -> AWS.CloudWatch
AWS.Lambda_Report -> AWS.CloudWatch
